OL,4,Cfragments traced by researcher
OL,6,FThe fate of "hidden" Stone of Destiny
OL,7,Ffragments has been traced by a
OL,8,Fresearcher who has been unravelling
OL,9,Fthe mysteries behind the ancient
OL,10,Fartefact.
OL,12,FProfessor Sally Foster's theory about
OL,13,Fthe puzzling "XXXV" Roman numeral on
OL,14,Fthe underside of the sandstone block
OL,15,Fhas also been published in an academic
OL,16,Fjournal.
