OL,4,Cfragments traced by researcher
OL,6,FProf Foster's research suggests Gray
OL,7,Fcollected 34 fragments of the original
OL,8,Fstone during this secretive work, as
OL,9,Fwell as potentially inscribing the
OL,10,Fnumeral for 35 on the stone itself as
OL,11,Fa light-hearted nod to his own role in
OL,12,Fthe story of the artefact.
OL,14,FFollowing a public appeal earlier this
OL,15,Fyear, her research has been published
OL,16,Fin The Antiquaries Journal as an
OL,17,Facademic paper.
