OL,4,Cfragments traced by researcher
OL,6,FThe lives of several fragments are
OL,7,Ftraced, some of which were gifted to
OL,8,FSNP politicians, including the late
OL,9,Fformer first minister Alex Salmond and
OL,10,Ftwo former MPs.
OL,12,FOne fragment travelled halfway across
OL,13,Fthe world to Australia and is stored
OL,14,Fin a museum.
OL,16,FProf Foster said: "This is not just
OL,17,Fany stone.
