OL,4,Cfragments traced by researcher
OL,6,FThe Stirling University researcher
OL,7,Falso discovered that Canadian
OL,8,Fjournalist and Calgary Herald editor
OL,9,FDick Sanburn was gifted a fragment and
OL,10,Fhad it mounted behind his desk.
OL,12,FProf Foster said: "With the likely
OL,13,Fperception of the fragments as being
OL,14,Fstolen property, few people opted to
OL,15,Fbrazenly flaunt and taunt with their
OL,16,Fpossession, except for some
OL,17,Fpoliticians.
