OL,4,Cfragments traced by researcher
OL,6,F"He had the rare and almost unique
OL,7,Fopportunity to access the underside of
OL,8,Fthe Stone, he had the means, he had
OL,9,Fthe sense of humour, and the number 35
OL,10,Fwould only have been meaningful and
OL,11,Fsignificant to him."
OL,13,FProf Foster says she is still keen to
OL,14,Fhear from people who may have
OL,15,Fknowledge of the fragments'
OL,16,Fwhereabouts.
